Packages 
Package Description
de.hshl.obj.data
Generic primitive utility classes, like an IndexRange and ArrayBuilder.Float.
de.hshl.obj.data.array
Dynamically sized Arrays for primitive ints or floats.
de.hshl.obj.loader
Provides a simple API for the core functionality of this library.
de.hshl.obj.loader.materials
Classes which are used to represent the MTL file after loading.
de.hshl.obj.loader.objects
Classes which are used to represent the OBJ file after loading.
de.hshl.obj.meta
Some classes meant to simplify the usage of the Java language in this project.
de.hshl.obj.wavefront
Classes which are very specific to loading wavefront data.
de.hshl.obj.wavefront.mtl
All classes that have no other purpose than loading an MTL file.
de.hshl.obj.wavefront.obj
All classes that have no other purpose than loading an OBJ file.
